    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>268932</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_060_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>パレスグドラの魔科学兵器の
被害はどうなっている</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>How much damage has Palace
Gudora's Mana Cannon caused?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>269128</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_060_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>詳細は不明ですが、
パレスグドラ国内には
甚大な被害が出ています</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We are unsure of the details. However,
Palace Gudora's territory has suffered
immense collateral damage.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>269128</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_060_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>それと……世界全域で、
マナの著しい減少が
観測されています</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Also... All over the world there have
been reports of Mana shortage crises.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>269236</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_060_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>自らの勝利のために
滅びを選んだか……
何ということを……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>So they chose a victory by means of
destroying themselves and everyone else.
How could it come to this...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>269352</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_060_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……マナを失った世界……
……わが星にとっては
『死』を意味する</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>With this much Mana loss around the
world...it means this planet will die...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>269512</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_060_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ご安心ください、ダオス様</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Do not worry, Sir Dhaos.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>269512</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_060_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>大樹カーラーンの根元に
『希望のひとしずく』が
残っております</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Deep inside the roots of the Great Kharlan
Tree, we still have the Guardian of the Tree,
our Tear of Hope, intact.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>269884</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_060_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>我が国の民だけ
救えるということか……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>All the news I hear about is from
my country's subordinates...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>269884</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_060_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>大国の王として……
貧しい二国に救いの手を
差し伸べることもできた……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Being the great King of the largest nation, I
should have been able to help smaller countries
with their economic problems and conflicts...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>269884</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_060_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>欲にまみれた武器商人たちを
止めることも
可能だったかも知れぬ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I should have been able to stop
the greedy weapon traders and
prevent possible civil wars...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>269884</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_060_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>しかし、それを
私は看過したのだ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yet, I averted my eyes and
allowed hell to break loose...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <BubbleId>3</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>269884</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_060_012&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>私は……なんと
不甲斐なき王だ……
いや……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I...am a despicable King for this country...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <BubbleId>4</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>270048</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_060_013&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>これから私は
大樹カーラーンを求めて
はるかな場所へ飛ぶ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>After this, I should attempt to secure
the Great Kharlan Tree's safety.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>270048</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_060_014&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>急がねばならぬ。
全てが、滅びる前に……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I need to act quickly...before
we are all doomed...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
